\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Your name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Mrs. Blanche Elizabeth Irons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Your address?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Stoke Hospital, Guildford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Year of marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 1911.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Year of birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 1889.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Birthplace?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Luton, Bedfordshire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How long did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I can't remember that really because my mother moved about a bit, you see. Still in Luton, though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So all the moves were in Luton until you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I was still living in Luton when we got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 , and lived in Luton still.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And why did you have to move around a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well my husband's health wasn't
 very good. It was the oil you see, got so in his system, and he thought well if he had a change, and so he came to Guildford and he was so enthralled with Guildford, that it was such a lovely with town, and we've been here ever since.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And before you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  did you move around because your father changed his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well no. You see, we used to go to different houses because the family grew bigger. There was five brothers and five sisters I had. So we went from one house to another that was larger, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And where did you come in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I was the second daughter, but I had a brother in between. My sister was the eldest, my brother next, then I was third in the family.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you had a lot of younger brothers and sisters. Were they born fairly close together?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 About a year and eight months in between. One was just walking as the other was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was that all of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you know how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No I don't know that, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When did he die?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 He was eighty six when he died. He died about 2 years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You don't know when he was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Still Luton. My grandparents were in Luton. They were straw hatters - made men's boaters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did your father work in the straw hat factory in Luton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. He done all different kinds. Gentleman's work and Very high class ladies work, felts and all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did he do any part-time work or only for the factory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 He was always in to the factory and only had what they earned.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did your father continue to live in Luton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes my father always lived in Luton, he never moved away from the town. I was the only one in the family that came away from home.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did he ever lose his job and become out of work if business was bad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No. Well you see their work was seasonable work - there used to be the dull times and the busy times. When the busy times was he used to start early in the morning 'til nine at night. And
 then perhaps you'd go a week with just doing samples and earn 2/6 perhaps. Go every day perhaps to see if there was work coming in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember how old your mother was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I remember she was only 59 when she died. And my youngest sister was 16
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember how old she was when she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No. I didn't remember anything like that. Course you know they didn't tell us children much in them days. You weren't allowed to read a paper th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11601437\charrsid10698579 ose}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  days
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your mother come from Luton, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I couldn't say that. But of course I think she must have been to Luton, she lived with her Granny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did she work before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes she used to work and she used to do it at home. She made beautiful la
dies' fancy hats at home. Machine then. Lovely hats they were. That was when I was little, right 'til I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 , she used to make the hats.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you don't know what work she did before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I suppose it was the same thing really. You usually keep on, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Could you tell me, after you children began arriving, did your mother go out at all to work? Or did she do all the work in the house at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I don't remember her doing much. Us girls used to do it, you see
. You see having a big family as the children come on and left school, you took the jobs on. I could cook and everything when I was thirteen. You left school when you was thirteen if you made the top grade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you enjoy your life at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. I didn't like it when I had to stop home wash days and help my eldest sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were there a lot of rooms in the house that you lived in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We had three large bedrooms. We had a big kitchen and a big scullery and a sitting room. We managed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did anyone else besides your parents and brothers and sisters live in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Good gracious, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You helped your mother in the house. Did your mother ever have anyone else to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I think an old aunt that I've got 
still alive, she's 94, I think, she used to come and do mum's washing for her 'til us older ones got big enough to do it. She was very good to us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did she look after the children at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I suppose we had to look after ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What did you call your aunt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Aunt Alice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you like her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes she was a nice aunt. I go and see her every time I get a chance to go to Luton to see her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And she did the washing for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes, 'cos she was young then you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did your father or mother help to make the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well yes she used to, but you see you don't remember that sort of thing, not when you're young. As long as you get the pinafore in your stocking at Christmas and some oranges and sweets, th
at was what you used to look for, We used to wear nice embroidered pinafores to school them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you don't know if your clothes were new or secondhand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh she used to buy me pinafores, yes. We only had one nice Sunday dress a year and used t
o outgrow it and the elbows would be gone when it was wore out. It was too much wore out to pass on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 It must have been difficult to provide you all with shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. Me mum used to look when we was in a bit late, and say "Have you been skipping!" "No, No Mum."
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Wearing out your shoes too fast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I don't remember. He was a real one fond of gardening. He used to grow our vegetables and flowers, he was very fo
nd of gardening, besides going to his work. He had a full-time job you see. And a nice bit of allotment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So he didn't have much time to do any decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what about the children, did you see much of him or was he too busy?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Oh yes. He used to come home. You see they had to come home to their meals every day them days. He used to come home regular dinner time -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did he ever read to you or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. He never had time for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did he have time to go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well he wasn't a man to go out much. 'Course they worked different hours then, they didn't have much time for pleasures.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So I don't suppose he had time to dress you or bath you or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well he did bath us and look after us when mother was in ill in hospital with fever ones. What couldn't be sent to gra}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14575522\charrsid10698579 n,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14575522\charrsid10698579 I was w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ith me grandmother for a little whi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14575522\charrsid10698579 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 e. He was a good father really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What things did you do regularly at home to help your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I used to do th
e shopping and help with the cooking and wash up. That was when I was at school. I could hear the whistle blowing, was supposed to be in school, and I was just finishing the washing up. And used to run like a hare to school. I was never there too soon.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And after you left school, what did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
My first job was to look after some people with babies. 'course I hadn't got enough at home! And they found I could do the cooking, I was thirteen, they found I could do the cooking so of course they
 left me to it. And then I gradually went into the factory, to learn the machining and I kept it up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And then did some of the other children look after the younger ones, when you had gone to the factory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. As you left school so you took the other one's place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And I suppose they helped them with dressing and feeding them, when they were very tiny?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You see you were brought up to do that automatic, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did any of them help you when you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well no. It was a fu
ll time job, you see, when you'd done work you used to come home and help with the housework. Us girls used to do it all and the boys used to do the polishing, the floors and all. And as you come on so you did the housework when you'd done the factory wor
k, you see, and the washing at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What time were you expected to go to bed in your school days?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Often times I was in a grocer's shop on a Saturday night at twelve o'clock. I remember the lady saying to me, "Now my dear, you should be in bed by now."
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What were you doing there - helping the grocer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No. There was always something mother just thinks of - "Oh. I forgot to get so and so, just pop to the shop." They were all so handy you see, you only had to go across the road and you was there. They were all little shops that served you themselves.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your mother put you to bed when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh, we all put ourselves to bed. We never had a fuss made of us them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Not even when you were little, you can't remember anyone else putting you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No. I remember having the mumps once, and I was so ill, and my mum just looked at me and said, "You do feel bad, don't you." I said "Yes." And I was propped up in the chair the side of her while she was machining. You 
see it's different when there's a big family of you, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I expect you had to share your bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Of course you did - three in a bed when you were little.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And that was the same for the rest of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes, we all had to share alike. We all had the same. No one made more of than the other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And where did you bath, in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. In front of the fire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How did they manage to get the water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Used to have to hot it in saucepans, you se}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11601437\charrsid10698579 e. From the gas stov}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 e.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have a bath night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Yes. My mother used to get the shopping Saturday nights and I used to bath the little ones whilst she was gone. Then with the nice big fire we used to do the ironing. Oh yes, you had to make good use of everything then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When did you have your clean clothes to put on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Every Sunday morning we had clean clothes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We all had it in the big kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were there any special occasions when you ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well Sundays. Mum used to get a big sponge - we used to call it Angels Food those days - but as we were older you see the family all used to come and the oldest ones that was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  and we always used to meet Sundays for Sunday tea. We used to have two sitting downs - two rooms - one was in one room and one was in another. There was so many of us you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well she used to cook in the scullery, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was it coal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We used to have the old fashioned range. It was lovely cooking those days. It cooked better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And where did you have breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 In the kitchen. We used to get up and didn't have much time to have much }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9399718\charrsid10698579 breakfast. Never be too early. It }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 was time to run off to work, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were all the members of the family present for breakfast or didn't you bother much with that meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well no, you see, some boys didn't wait for breakfast, they used to have to be at work by 6 o'clock in the mornings them days. So they used to take a piece with them, you see, and then have it when they like come home you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What did you usually eat before you went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We had a piece of bread and home dried lard - it was lovely them days, you know. We never had margarine but we had 
the old home dried lard and it was really gorgeous.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What would you have for your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Mother used to make nice beef puddings in basins. And the boys used to have nice long pasties fitted across their plates with meat inside and they used
 to be delicious. They didn't think they'd had dinner unless they'd had one of those that reached all half }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11601437\charrsid10698579 w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
ay over the plate. Yes they were lovely dinners them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what did you have in the evening when you came back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well sometimes we use
d to have just a snack like you do, bread and cheese, or something like that. Like they do today. Sometimes fish and chips, 'cos you had a nice piece of fish for id them days, and a ha'porth of chips, more then you'd get for half a crown now.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your mother bake her own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We used to have a lovely loaf. Cottage loaves they called them. 2 1/2d a loaf and it was lovely bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You said you had vegetables in your garden. Did she bottle any vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did she make pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did she make her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No. She used to buy it. Well you see jam was only 6d a pound them days. And the butter, when we got older we used to have butter, was 11 1/2d a pound.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did they buy any fruit or vegetables, or did you just have what you had from the garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
We all had all our own vegetables, potatoes and all our green vegetables, and plenty of celery at Christmas. We used to fight shy of who should wash the celery Christmas time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have any tinned vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We never thought of having tinned stuff them days, oh dear no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you keep any hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Mum used to have one - just one, that used to lay nice brown eggs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No pigs or goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Who looked after the hen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well i
t was only the one, you see, Mum had that she used to like to have just the one, just to eat the odds and ends if there was any left. There wasn't much as a rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And how many times a week did you have meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We had it every day. And we always us
ed to have to have a nice spare rib of pork on Sunday and a wing rib of beef. I know when I was a little girl my Mum said "You go to the butcher and tell him I want a wing rib of beef." I used to say to myself a wing rib of beef, all the way, and then I u
sed to say it the wrong way round when I did get there. And the butcher used to laugh and say he knew what me mum meant.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what about extra meat, like a rabbit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes, you could get a rabbit for about eleven pence then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 That would be from the shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. The butchers or in the market. Yes we always had plenty of rabbits. You could get a chicken for half a crown.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember if your mother gave herself less food that she gave to all of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well you don't notice that when you're young. You don't notice what mother has so long as you've got yours, that's all you worry about.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 But your father, did he have a bigger portion do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. She used to serve him, I suppose, naturally. We didn't take notice, so long as you got yours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were you allowed to talk during meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We never dared talk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked, or did you have to have a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You had just what your mother give you. You never had no choice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And supposing you left some of it uneaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We never left it my dear, there was never too much to leave.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 If there was something on the table you wanted, could you ask someone to pass it to you, or did you have to wait until it was offered?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well you just asked could you have it. But there was usually one for everybody, it was just shared out like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. You couldn't get a second helping. You had to be satisfied.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes, you had to behave yourself.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Could you bring books or toys to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh dear no. We never had toys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You could leave the table when you see the others, you didn't leave too soon in case something else was coming. You waited to make sure.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 All the family sat down together, did they, for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes. When they was all home. When we was school children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you always sit in the same place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your mother serve the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes, mum always used to see that we was alright. But when we got older we, the one that was home first, dinner time us
ed to do the sharing out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what order were you served in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well we always used to have our meat and vegetables and gravy first. And then we'd have our sweet afterwards, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And would it go to your father first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes, dad always had to be served first. Same with a cup of tea. Dad always had to have the tea out first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Who came next after dad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well we was all served round as we come, you see, as we sat at the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And how did your younger brothers and sisters manage? Who gave them their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well us older ones used to help them, you see. Like it comes natural to you when there's a lot of you, you see, helping one another.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes a very good mother, she was. Very kind. She used to say how lucky }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11601437\charrsid10698579 w
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 e was for a big family that none of us was really worried with health and that you see
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did she show her affection to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. She didn't. No we didn't have any fuss made, but ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 If you were worried could you go and talk to her?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well you'd say "Oh, I don't half feel funny." She'd say "Well you can't be right" and laugh at you, and that's how it used to happen, you see. You never made a fuss. She'd say, "Oh well, you'll be alright tomorrow."
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You couldn't take your worries to your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 He was never there you see. He was mostly at work you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well we was always good to them, because you thought the world of your mothers and fathers them days, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did your parents bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in certain ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes, we always had to behave ourselves and help one another, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Supposing another child hurt you, did they say you should hit back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no. We had to fight our own battles. We had to put up with it if we didn't agree with the children. It was no good going home to mum.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you children would grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Mother used to say, "Never do wrong and always tell the truth. Then you've got nothing to be afraid of wherever you go to live there'll be always someone that will know you."
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So she thought that was very important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. Well it really was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What did they think about swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no, my mother never heard any swearing at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When the grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes we used to join in each conversation with each other, you know, natural.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And if you did something your parents disapproved of, what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I don't think we ever remembered doing anything like that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You don't remember what punishments you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh my dad never hit us. No. He'd just grumbl
e at us and say hadn't we got more sense. But otherwise you only had to be spoke to once, or a look was enough.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would this be by your father or mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well it was dad really. He would say "Where's your sense, you know better than that." But you didn't need telling twice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would you say that you received the ideas you had about how to behave from both your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well no. I remember saying I'd like something one day and my dad "Oh well my girl when you go out to work and earn it you can have it."

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have any birthday presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Anything special to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. No fuss made of us really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No little friends to tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No there was plenty without the friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about Christmas Day, was that different in anyway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well yes. We used to look for our stockings, with plenty of oranges and apples and nuts, and a new pinafore. And we was quite happy. You didn't expect toys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have any musical instruments in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes, we had a piano, and a little harp. And we had a gramophone with a horn.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Who played them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I used to play by ear. One of my sisters did have lessons. But I stated and my dad sa
id "For goodness sakes leave off that row." He had friends that was musical, you see. He used to entertain friends as we got older. And they used to come into the home and practice for the concerts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was any member of your family able to sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We
ll no. Unless it was me. They used to ask me to sing at the mission. One gentleman I worked for at the factory, he was a preacher, and he used to say "Dolly, will you come to the mission Sunday?" and I didn't realise and said alright. Then he'd say "Miss 
Armitage will give us a solo." And I used to give him a look but I couldn't do no other but get up and sing one of the hymns for them.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes. Sunday nights. Yes we used to have quite a good time. Al
l of them used to come up and we would sit, and my eldest sister that did keep the practice up she used to play and we would all sing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your parents play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Dear, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were there any books in the house, or newspapers or magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well my dad used to have the Black and White, that was when the war was on, you see. When I was a little girl. I can remember that. The Black and White, some paper that had, like they do now, when the war was on, with all the Boer War n
ews. And you could have had them made into a big volume, you see, if you liked, but I don't remember him ever doing it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you ever remember your mother and father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. There were never time, you know, really. Nor for Mother
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did they ever read aloud to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Or to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember a funeral in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We didn't have to take interest in anything like that those days, you know. Children was kept from all that sort of worry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you go out visiting neighbours or friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Only my aunt I used to go and see. That's all. But otherwise my mother never had time to go out much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you go with someone or by yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well we used to know our way about you see, living in the town we knew all the roads.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever go out with your father, alone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
He used to take us out once a year. He used to have a wagonette when I was a little girl and he used to take us out just that one day and we used to go to
 London Colney the other side of St. Albans, and that was once a year in the summer. He used to do that when we was little, that's the only time I remember.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did everybody go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 All the children went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 This was a real holiday!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes! That was our one thing to look forward to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How did you spend Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Doing the shopping. And, as I was telling you, when I got older and left school, I used to bath the children and do the ironing what was left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What happened on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I used to do the cooking. Make the pastry for mum and see to the cooking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have different clothes on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes we always had to have Sunday dress. You see we used to wear that for about twelve months on Sundays 
and then when it got short for us we used to wear it to school, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about your activities on Sundays? Did you ever play games or did your parents think it was wrong to work or play on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 She never said anything. 'Course she alway
s had to do a certain amount naturally, but I used to go to Sunday School. Yes we used to go to Sunday School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you go to church or chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We used to go to church and we used to go to the Baptist Sunday School in the afternoons, you see
. And sometimes I used to go to the Salvation Army. When you're children you go where your friends go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your mother or father go to church with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I don't know. There was always so many little babies you see. My mother didn't have a chance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were there any Sunday School outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We used to go to Hatfield Park those days. We used to sit on the grass all of us and have tea brought round to us, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And were there any other activities organised by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Not that I can remember.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. My oldest brother belonged to Luton Church Choir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would he be paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I don't know. I can't remember that. I don't think so. That's the church our Queen goes to when she goes to
 Luton, you see. Lovely church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did the church run any temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I couldn't tell you. I don't think they did them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you belong to any other club organised by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Never had time to go to anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No, we never had time for grace. You never all sat down together sometimes you see, specially as you got older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about saying prayers? Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No we used to just say it if we wanted to. My mother was always so busy, you see, working and one thing and another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You didn't have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your father take any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I think he was a good old conservative. That's the only thing. I didn't understand much about it them days, but I do remember that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about your mother, do you remember if she was interested?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No she never had time for anything like that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember your parents voting in a General Election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Well you see we was never brought into anything like that not in them days. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 But you think they would have voted conservative if they had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. My dad always said there was plenty of work about when the conservatives was in. He always said that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11601437\charrsid10698579 I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 remember him saying that once when he was arguing a little bit with somebody. But I do remember that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from t
heir employers. Do you know if your father felt like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well no, because you see, there was all the different factories and they used to go when one was dull to another factory. It wasn't like it is today. They was all little individual men, got their own small places, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When your parents were not doing their work, what were they doing with their spare time if they had any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well they used to go to backwards and forwards to see if there was any work for them, you see. And just come
 home meal times and perhaps wander round and see if somebody had got work in a different factory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your mother ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. She never left us to do anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your father stay at home in the evenings when he got back from work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well he was too tired, you see, to go out. They used to work 'til eight o'clock, or nine, all hours you see. They had to to earn the money, for when there wasn't any work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So he didn't go to any clubs or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did he have time to take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Gardening was his sport. He was always having to dig the garden and plant things you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How did you get on with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well we all thought the world of one another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was there one that you felt particularly fond of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you play with your brothers and sisters only, when you were a child? Or with neighbours' children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Now we could go out to play. There wasn't the traffic about there is today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Where did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh just out in the streets. So that we was handy if mother wanted us for anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you play in your garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We always had a garden you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember what games you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Skippi
ng. We used to have a top. Hoops. In them days we used to run along with a hoop. If we went to get anything from the shop we used to bowl our hoop there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Could you play with anyone you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes. Along as they was nice children, you see, my mum didn't mind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. There was nothing like that then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have any hobbies when you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We just went to school and we had reading, writing and arithmetic, and we used t
o be able to have a knitting lesson or sewing lesson. And when the cookery first started it was just one afternoon or a few hours in the morning a week. That was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you keep any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We usually had a rabbit, that's all. And just one chicken. But we didn't have many rabbits because mum didn't like rabbits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever help with the gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We were never allowed to touch the garden, that was Dad's job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you go for walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
 Just to Sunday School and back again. Never had time, there was always the children to look after you see, you couldn't very well go far.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Didn't you have time to take part in any sports yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Or go to theatres or concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We wasn't allowed to do anything. I didn't go to any theatre 'til I was about thirteen.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you have any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well we used to have a penny a week and then my mother gave me tuppence once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What did you spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well
 I used to have a farthing at a time - and have a Spanish ladder, two strips joined together like that for a farthing. And we used to get a quarter of sweets for a penny. A quarter of chocolate drops for a penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When your mother was ill, I think you said your aunt came to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well she used to just do the washing. That was when we were very tiny. I remember my mother telling me she used to come and do her washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What happened when your mother had a new member of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Us older ones used to have to take the job on you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your parents have any relatives, apart from this aunt, living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I don't remember anybody coming. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did they have any friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. It wasn't like it is today, you know. You didn't have people come in and out, like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did people ever call in without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your parents ever go out to visit friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. It was a full time job you know when you had a big family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Many people divide society into different social classes or groups. In that time did you think of some people as belonging to one social class and some to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I don't remember anything like that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you can't remember thinking about other people who might belong to a different group from your self
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well you didn't have any interest only your own family, you see, then.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were you ever told to curtsey or show respect to anyone in particular?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Not in the town. It's \{ILLEGIBLE\} Out in the country they used to do that. But not in the town. We didn't have that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember who were considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I don't think that anyone was really very important to anyone else, them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What sort of people would you say went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well they always seemed to be proud people to me, when I was young. They always seemed to be so very proud.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was it the same in the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. They seemed more friendly, when I used to go to the Sunday School, and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So do you think that the people who went to church felt a bit more superior?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes, I did then when I was younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were some families thought of as rough and others as more respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We never had to mix with people that was drink or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember any distinction like this between craftsmen and Labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We wasn't brought up to think any difference. They was all working people and someone had to do it, the lower job you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No, she was a very nice person. My dad was too. He'd give to anybody or do anything, for 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was it possible to move from one group to another? Can you remember anyone who did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember people being described as a 'real gentleman' or a 'real lady'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Oh yes. We was always scared stiff of a policeman. Oh yes, they'd only got to look at us. We were frightened to death of a policeman them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When you were naughty, did your mother ever say 'I'll call a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Oh no. My dad called one in because my brother played truant one day. And he came in the house to frighten my brother and I started crying and said "Don't take him away!" I remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How did the policeman treat the people, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well no. We didn't do anything to need to know in that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you remember anything about your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We didn't interest ourselves in anything like that when we was children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you feel now that your parents had to struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well they did. 'Cos my mother did you see. 'Cos there used to be months my dad didn't earn anything hardly. That's why he had to work so hard when the season was on. His was seasonable work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember what difference there was in the home when your father hadn't got to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well mother used to say 'I don't know what we shall do, your dad hasn't had any work again this week.' And you never had help them days. You only had what you earned you see. No unemployment business them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Nothing from the Guardians?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 The parish or any charity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Nothing at all, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your mother or father belong to any savings club when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 But what about sickness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no. Nothing like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I think you said they belonged to the Prudential?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. Insurance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 For the funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes, just for funerals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And that was for all of you children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes all of us. Just about a penny a week it used to be, or tuppence, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Your parents must have had quite an effort to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We had dull seasons you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 As a child do you remember what you felt about that? Were you aware they were having a struggle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Yes, because mother used to look at our shoes and say "Have you been skipping again?" She was worried for fear we'd wear them out too quick.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you realised she was worried?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I think you said that the people who went to church were less friendly than the people who went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well they seemed to be, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about the teachers and farmers and people like that? Did they go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I couldn't tell you that, because it just used to be our own little way of going to Sunday School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you really didn't come into contact not with the clergy or the teachers very much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Before you went to school were you ever given lessons by your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes, I used to do cooking for mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Cooking lessons. Any other sort of lessons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No. I used to be given the job to do it and told just what to do. And when I was at school, I was about twelve, this cookery teacher she wanted me to go in and be a cookery teacher becaus
e I seemed to know more than most of them you see. Well of course doing it at home I had all the insight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I was three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 That was very young!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. They did go to school at three them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you just go in the mornings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How long were you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 All day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you go home for lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We all lived close to our schools those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you came home in the middle of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. Twelve o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Then how long before you had to be back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Back to school again at half past one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would that be a church school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No they was all just board schools.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did they have boys as well as girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes they had one part for
 the boys and one part for the girls. And we stayed at the same school from when we started 'til we left school. You had no mess about like they do today. 'Course we didn't have buses them days, and we was always living handy to our schools.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you lived quite close to school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And who went with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No one, because we could see our school almost, or hear the children out to play you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So just you brothers and sisters went together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We all went to the same school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember what you thought of school? Did you enjoy it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes. I used to cry when I had to stop away, when I got older, to help my oldest sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember anything about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes I always seemed to like all the teachers. We had very nice teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember if they emphasised certain things as important in life, such as manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes, we always had to behave ourselves, we daren't do any other. It was the way we were brought up you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have to be tidy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes. We always had to have a clean pinafore. One special Pinafore with all }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9399718\charrsid10698579 embroidery}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  just for school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And punctual?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what about ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well just ordinary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did they correct you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what happened if you were late for school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You didn't dare be late. We used to have to line up in rows outside you see and then we used to march in.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what happened if your teachers disapproved of something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I don't think I ever remember being told anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember anyone else that they punished and what that punishment would be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. But if you were punished you had to stop in after school. That was the only thing. Of course you didn't like that, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What would that be for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 If you were naughty. If perhaps they see you talking, see. When you were supposed to be working or silent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would the punishments be the same for the boys as the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I expect so. Course they were in a different part of the building.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 They didn't work with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no. Boys were separate those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your parents take an interest in your school work? Did they ever talk to you about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. They just left it to the teachers you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did they ever have meetings in those days of teachers and parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No. Not as I remember. Well they all seemed very placid and happy, you know. You didn't hear any disagreement. Of course when you're children you don't realise anything like that you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You don't remember your parents going to the school to any meeting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Only to the Primrose league once a year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 That was a sort of club, I think, called the Primrose league.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Anything to do with school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Nothing at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about the other children did they come from similar types of home to your own or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes they was all poor people. What we'd call poor people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We were all treated the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember if there were any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no. We always used to have to run home and do jobs, you see. As soon as you got home there was always something to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were there any children who seemed to left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Thirteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would you have liked to have stayed on longer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I would have done, but I knew my mother wante
d me home, you see, with the babies. There was always two. One that couldn't walk and another }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14575522\charrsid10698579 one}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 , There was always a }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14575522\charrsid10698579 \{ILLEGIBLE\}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  of napkins waiting for me to wash.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you go to any evening classes or part-time education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. My evening classes was at home. That's where I had to learn all my stuff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Looking back now do you have any regrets about your education? Would you have liked to have gone on longer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I would have done, I liked school. \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you feel you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9399718\charrsid10698579 benefited}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  from having been to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Oh yes. Well our main things was reading, writing and arithmetic. And we used to have sewing classes and we could knit if we wanted to. And one morning we went to a cookery class but that was at another school and we had to walk there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 While you were at school, did you have any part-time job or any means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no. Never had time for that!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Now could I ask you about the first job you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 The first job I had, my mother let me go and help the person that had the straw business, to look after the two children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How did you get that job? Would it be through your parents? Or the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no, schools didn't get you anything them days, you got your own little jobs.
 Might be in the paper, you see, or you might hear of some one who wanted some one. I just went. I was so little I couldn't see over the top of the pram.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And then the lady found I could cook so of course I was left a little extra to do like that, yo
u see. But I wasn't there long. I used to get 4/6 a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And how long did you work each day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I went in the morning 'til seven o'clock at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what about Saturdays and Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I went Saturday but I didn't go Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have a half day at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We was lucky if we got Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember whether you felt satisfied with 4/6 a week or whether you felt you should have had more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well it was no good to think you w
anted more. There wasn't enough work for people those days. If you didn't take the job there was always somebody else ready you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember if you gave any of this money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Mother had all the money - I used to have a penny a week to spend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So that just went in the housekeeping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We was only too pleased to give it to our mothers you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And was anybody else working in the home that you went to help in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
You didn't see much of them you see. Only at meal times 'cos they left you with the children you see. You just took the children out and just looked after the children and see that they had their food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember what you felt about your employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I didn't take any notice. As long as you knew you were doing your duty that was all that bothered you really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were you happy in the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. I wasn't there long because I took up me ordinary straw hat work after that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So how long were you in this job, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 About twelve months, nearly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember if you felt differently about school after you'd been working a little while?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. You see you take everything in your stride. Things just come and go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Could you tell me a little bit about your straw hat work. Did you get that job through your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No. You'd see the advert for a machinist or trimmer in the paper and you'd just go to the factory and they'd take you on and you'd learn it th
rough the others you see. You'd watch the others or they'd give you a sample of what you had to do. How it's to be trimmed, and that's that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What exactly did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Trim the hats.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Not make them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No, you started at trimming ha
ts. Then I thought that wasn't quick enough for me so I started learning the machining. So I machined the hats then and I done that right 'til I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 That was making up the hats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. Making them with the straw plaits.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what hours did you work? Do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
When it was a busy season, we used to get samples out early in the year and then they used to depend on the buyers to give 'em big orders for the samples all the different shapes and sizes, and if it was so busy you'd
 be there at seven in the morning 'til nine at night. And no restrictions, you was only too glad to do it. To earn all the money you could because you knew it would slacken off you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And would that include Saturday or Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh you'd work Saturday 'til tea time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you have a half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. You had what you earned. You didn't have any half days. You didn't get any pay you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Just Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Just Sundays. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No Mondays with pay?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No, no unemployment or anything like that
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember what you were paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
If you was given a dozen hats, you'd perhaps get half a crown a dozen. When you'd done them you took them in and they'd give you another issue a head of plait and a block to work to and when y
ou'd done that that was booked in a book to you, you see, but you only had what you earned. If you was lazy you didn't have any money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So it was really piece work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes, we never had anything else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you give that money to your mother too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes all of it. 6d a week back for my pocket.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What were the other people like in the place where you were making the hats and working on them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 They was all jolly you know. We had to shout to one another over the noise of the machines. 
There used to be rows of us, you see, facing. Like machines and another lot would be there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How did you get on with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh alright. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what about your employer there, did he treat you well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well they was just the foreman you s
ee and he went to you when you wanted more work and they was just ordinary men to do it, you see, just special ones to give the work out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember what he was like - how you got on with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well you didn't have a chance to do any other t
han just give it you quick and off you was, you couldn't be quick enough to get back to your job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you like }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14575522\charrsid10698579 him?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well, yes. You didn't have time to, you know, know whether you liked them or not. He just give it you and the quicker you was gon
e the better. You couldn't afford to hinder time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what did you feel about the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well we liked it. You see my grandparents done it, my father done it, it was in the family you see. My mother used to make beautiful hats. So you see it was just our way of living.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember if this work affected your attitude towards school at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well no. It was nothing like school, you see, at all. We'd left school and forgot all about school really then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You went on with that work then until you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Then what happened after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ? Do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I didn't go into the factory for a while, but of course my husband then was 21 and I was 22. His wage was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16736968 \'a3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 2 a week and that was a big wage, he was a high rate man at the time. And we used to get 1 cwt of coal for a shilling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you didn't work for a while after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Not for a while. But being so busy at home with the rushing backwards and forwards, we used to have to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11345442\charrsid10698579 walk}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
 home at lunch time, it was just one rush, you see. But I got so as I was at a loose end, all I done was scrub my kitchen floors. We had a nice little new cottage 6/6 a week rent. No rates or anything to worry about. And I got so tired of being on that e
xtreme that I went back into the factory again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you stay there until you came to Guildford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well no. I left off and I started, when I was going to have my baby, to work at home. I'd been }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  three years when she was born and I couldn't g
o into the factory then so I had work at home, and that's how it was. And when she was five months old I came to Guildford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you work at all after you came to Guildford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. There was no work here you see, that I'd done. No I couldn't really with her to look after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So apart from having a training period in the factory, to learn how to trim and make the hats you didn't have any other training?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you belong to any trade union or any group like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11345442\charrsid10698579 I always }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember if you felt that employers and workers had the same interest or different interests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well nobody bothered about you so long as you done the work. That was all they troubled.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you feel that there were divisions of interest among the workers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well no, you see, in them days you was all the same. You all took the work on and just carried on the same
 as anybody else, you see, all having to work for your living. You all done the same almost.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you think that having full time work changed your attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well you get that different interest you see. You don't have time for 
anything else but work and go home and do jobs when you get home and all that sort of thing. We wasn't waited upon. We all had to do our share when we got home with the lot of us you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you find when you started full time work that your relationship with your parents changed at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No we always thought a lot of our parents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about your brothers and sisters. Did it make a lot of difference to your relationship with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We all thought a lot of one another you see. We worried about each other if one wasn't very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And you said you had Sundays off, so did you then spend them any differently when you were working all the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Used to do the cooking for mum, when I was at home. Yes I used to reckon to make all the pastry. Make the beds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you go to Sunday School?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
I did before I got old enough to have to stop at home to do things. Yes, when my little friends went I went. Sometimes it was the Baptist chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 But that was when you were still at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you to go church or chapel after you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well where my friends went I went. I went sometimes to the Salvation Army, sometimes to the Baptist Sunday School. That's how things are you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11345442\charrsid10698579 just }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 \{ILLEGIBLE\}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11345442\charrsid10698579  when you are children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And when you were older?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 One gentleman I worked for he'd got a small business and he was a preacher and he asked me one day to go to the Railway Mission, }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11345442\charrsid10698579 and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 \{ILLEGIBLE\} so I said alright \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 After you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
 how did you and your husband manage the housekeeping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I always followed my mother's advice. She said "Now my girl, you're going to get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 
Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  but I must tell you this, as you make your bed so 
you must lay. Don't go to a shop with a book if you have groceries, just go and pay for what you have else you'll be buying things you can't afford to pay for at the end of the week. \{ILLEGIBLE\} Never lend, never borrow and don't \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 in anybody els
e's house - if they're ill and want you to help that's a different thing." And I've always kept to all that. "And don't take all your money out, what your husband's wages are, put your rent on one side, put all what you've got to pay out on one side, and 
just get your shopping so that you know you pay for everything you have and you'll find you'll be on the right side." And I've always done that, always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you know what your husband earned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16736968 \'a3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
2 a week. That was a top rate man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How much of that would he give to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 He gave me }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16736968 \'a3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
1 'til I found out he was earning }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16736968 \'a3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 2. Then I soon kicked up I'll tell you, and he give me more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you then discuss how the money should be spent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I left him to pay the rent and buy all the things
, I thought it would be a lesson. And he said "Oh I've had enough of this mate, I haven't paid any rent for a fortnight." I said "Well you get on with it - you can stretch it." That cured him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You said you had a cottage, when you were first }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 , how many rooms would there have been in that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Two bedrooms, and two rooms downstairs and a nice scullery. 6/6 a \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would you have anybody else living there? A lodger or anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Not then, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And you looked after the house yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You didn't have any help with it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you do all your washing at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about your clothes - do you remember if you made any or if you bought them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well you could always buy your things pretty reasonable then, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would you buy them new or second-hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 At the shops in Luton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your husband buy his clothes as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. They used to get a bonus at the Vauxhall where he worked and so they had a nice bit every \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 while and he used to just buy what he wanted for himself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When any clothes needed repairing would you do the repairing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You used to wear them out and then get some new ones. \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well you see you could get a pair of shoes mended cheaper than what they are today. You could buy a pair of men's sandals from Marks and Spencers for 5/6d.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 If your shoes wanted repairing would you take them to a boot repairer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would your husband repair them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We took them to the shop to have them done properly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your husband have time to help you in the house at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Good gracious, no. He used to like to go fishing if he did get a chance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you did all the cleaning and cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes I did everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what about decorating?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well the landlords would do that for you, if you wanted anything done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And the repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about fires - would your husband get the coal in or would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I would. I'd been used to all that sort of thing at home. Girls done it the same as the boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about firewood and all that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well we used to get two bundles for 1 1/2d in them days. 1/2d a bundle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you bought it at the shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Now you had one daughter didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have any other children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I had another one when she were two and a half, but that was a blue baby and that died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your husband ever help you with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. No. He left it all to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 As they grew older would he take them out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes, he'd take the one, you see we only had that one. He'd take her out in the pram or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would he tell her stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would he ever read aloud to her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. He didn't do anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 As your daughter got older did she help you in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. I taught her to do little things and cooking and all that. \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember what time she was put to bed when she was small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Just put them to bed when they're tired. No rules or regulations, them days.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did she go to bed by herself or did you put her to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 She used to go to bed by herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did she have a bedroom to herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And you and your husband slept in the other bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what about bath night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well we used to have a bath in front of the fire and bath like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would that be the same as you did in your own home on Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you had bath night on Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And that meant clean clothes on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. Oh yes. We've always had clean shoes ready on Sunday and clean clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You told me earlier someth
ing of how you spent your spare time, did you continue to spend your spare time in the same way when you were working full time? Did you continue to help your mother or did you do different things then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no. There was never time, there was always p
lenty waiting for us at home. You see my mother wasn't very strong so us girls had to do all the work and the washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you go out in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Not much, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Where would you go to if you did go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well when I first knew my husband
 we used to go round the country for a walk. And we used to say to the other girls at the factory "Are you going out tonight?". "I'll meet you Flo." And we'd all go round by the road and the park and have a walk and there used to be two or three couples.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And then did you bring them home afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh No. No. Not 'til just before I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 . I wasn't allowed to bring them home.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you'd go out for a walk with them - would you go back to their homes then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We just walked around and they left you outside your house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would your parents meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
In the finish they would. We used to take them home and they used to have wait for us while we got ready 'cos we was always full of work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your parents expect to know where you were when you went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We didn't have to be out late those days. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You told me you were 22 when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How long had you known your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 About two years then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And where did you meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well they come to live next door to us and that was how I met him. We used to talk down the garden and my mother said "Why don't you two go out if you're going, not stand down there talking on each side of the garden wall." And that's how it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And where did they come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 My husband was born almost next door but one to me but I didn't know him 'til later like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So they were a Luton family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you save up money before getting }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well we saved a bit. My husband he saved a bit and what we hadn't got before we was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 
Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  we saved and gradually added on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your parents help you in setting up house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no. We had not many wedding presents them days.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How long were you engaged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I wasn't engaged. I wouldn't have an engagement ring.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How many years did you live in the cottage after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I lived for about eighteen months in one, and that was about a 
mile and half from my husband's work and then we moved nearer to the school that I used to go to. Next door but one to the school I went to, and that's where my daughter was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How long were you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I was there 'til - I should say I was there about two years. Then I come to Guildford after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Where did you live in Guildford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
In Station Road. My husband got one room there and we used to walk miles there to try and get a house but we couldn't. And the same person had a row of co
ttages that she used to own and one of these come empty so we moved there but they was some old places, my word. They're all pulled down now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How long were you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I was there for about two years. More than two years then I managed to ge
t a house in Manor Road. And that had water under the cellar and it got as how I couldn't use my legs because of the damp. Yes. So my husband; they had some cottages in Middleton Road and he put in for one of those and we got one of those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And were you there a long time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. Ten years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You came to Guildford when?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
 in 1911 and came to Guildford on the Christmas of 1914. War had just started in the August.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 After you left that house then, in 1924, where did you go them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
I went to stay with my dad for a little while because he wasn't very well. Then I came back again and my husband got me another house in Manor Road. And then he got me another house under Dennis's where he worked and we was there ten years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So your husband worked at Dennis's when you came to Guildford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What did he do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Engineers turner he was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what did he do in Luton before you moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 He was the same, engineers turner, at the Vauxhall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How long did he stay in Dennis's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 He was there nearly thirty years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was that until he retired?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well he was taken ill and then of course he couldn't do any more, he died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So he didn't have any other job after leaving Dennis's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 He never left
 you see, he was took ill. When he did leave it was through illness, and he gradually went down and just passed away. That was 1944.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When he was working at Dennis's did he do any part-time job as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no. No. He had a heavy job that was why. He was glad to get away from the oil and the smell.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What do you feel your husband thought about his work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 He was apprenticed to it, you see, and he didn't know any other. He never complained.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Could you give me the date of birth of your daughter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 31}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \super\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 st}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  July 1914.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And the little baby that you lost?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Another little girl. 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \super\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 rd}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  December 1916, and she died the 8}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \super\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  January 1917.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were both babies born at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. Yes. You see they were both what you might as well say, war
 babies. The war was on then it was a job to get anyone. Doctors was all called up and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you know what to expect in childbirth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I had a very bad time with my daughter. And it was a very hard birth with this baby. And they couldn't m
ake out what it was, but I think she was too long before she was born.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Too long in labour, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have a doctor both times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I had to have a doctor. A real good doctor at Luton. They said it was marvelous I was alive.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did your husband help you at all with the birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No, my mother used to come down and just give me a hand, you see. But I had a neighbour that come in to do for me, with my second baby. After the nurse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How long were you in bed, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When the first baby was born I was on my back for a month. I couldn't get off my back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what happened to the house while you were in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well my mother, she'd send the children down you see, \{ILLEGIBLE\} all sorts of things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did any of the relations, apart from your mother, or your neighbours help you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well no, just me mother. You see I had a very old couple live next to me when my first baby was born. But then here, with the second one, I was in Guildford you see, the midwife come in then, because we didn't have the jubilee nurses then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And so the midwife delivered the baby. Did she come in and see you after the birth at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes. She just come after 'til she knew I was alright. That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you breast feed your baby - the first one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. She was a prize baby, she weighed ten pounds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you enjoy feeding her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well yes. But she got on. She was a big baby and she kept it up. She won prizes and all sorts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have any difficulty in breast feeding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 If you got worried or needed advice who would you ask?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You had to ask your own common sense them days, you didn't have anyone you could run to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You just had to manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. You'd just get on with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 If the baby was asleep, would you wake it for a feed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. You didn't do that them days. They'd let you know when they was hungry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And if it cried before the normal feeding time, would you feed it then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well you would, because you'd think to yourself it was hungry because sometimes we're more hungry than others aren't we.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What would you do if it didn't seem to want it's food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You didn't worry. You'd think to yourself they used next time. We didn't fuss with them like they do today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember how long you'd let it go on feeding if it wanted to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well they left off automatically when they was satisfied.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember when you first gave it solid food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. You used to give the b
ath biscuits then. You just soaked them in milk. They was just about the size of a cup and they used to be nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And how long would you feed the baby, do you remember, when you weaned her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Just ordinary you see. We'd }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9399718\charrsid10698579 mash}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  her food up. Never had tinned food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How long did you feed her for? How many months?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 About eight, you know, as soon as they start to have like any other things. Like soft sloppy food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember how you did wean her, would you stop it, feeding her, gradually or did you do it fairly sudden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no. You'd do it gradually. They sort of weaned themselves in a way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did she take to it well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember what you felt about a baby crying? Whether you thought it did any harm to cry?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well my baby cried, the first one, for three months. Doctor said she'd have to be took away if she kept on, she was a screamer. It was the way she was born, she was cut about so and pulled about terrible. That was why it was I suppose. It was a worry. 'Co
s I couldn't sit up or do anything. Used to have to pull her about. They used to have binders about them those days and I used to have to pull her across one way and another. Still we got over it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Later on, when the baby was naughty, would you remember what you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No. You don't take any notice. Just the natural way. We've all got 'em you see. You'd think to yourself oh well it's one of them things, she's like her dad, got a fair bit of temper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 But I suppose later on as she got a bit older she would be naughty sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. They all do, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How would you deal with that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Just let them get on with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever punish her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what about your husband, would he help with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well there was only the one really. No. He just let me. I was mother and father too. He never interfered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So he didn't help to get her to sleep if she was crying?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Or attend to her in the night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. They didn't trouble like they do today, you know. \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 After you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
, where did you have }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9399718\charrsid10698579 your meals}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
We had them in our sitting room, like. There was two rooms besides the scullery. And my husband would never have a meal where the sink was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you had it in the sitting room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 In one of them. You see we had the two rooms. We called them the kitchens then, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And if you had a special occasion, such as visitors, would you eat in a different room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We never did make fuss you see. If we had anybody it was usually our own and they took us as we always was, you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you cook in the scullery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We had a gas stove you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What time did you have breakfast in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 My husband used to have to run off to work at six o'clock. Be there at six, so he used to go off at quarter past five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did he take food with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did he have anything before he left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No he'd take a snack to have and perhaps have a cup of tea, you see. Perhaps have something 
quick. He'd fill his can up with tea, but I never had to do that for him - he used to do it himself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You and your daughter would have breakfast after he'd gone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well sometimes I'd have a piece of bread and butter and I'd cook her an egg if she wanted it. Just what she fancied. Bread and jam.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about Sundays, did you have anything different on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We used to have bacon. My husband used to have bacon or he'd have a duck's egg if there were any duck's eggs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And Sunday midday, did you have a special meal then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We always had our joint. He always liked a half a leg of lamb.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what would you have Sunday evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Bread and cheese.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would that be the same as you'd have on other days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what about bread? Did you buy your bread or did you make it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We bought our bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you make anything at home like jam or pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. I made all my own pickles and jam, too.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you do any bottling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. No bottling
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about wine or beer or medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. No we didn't have anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you grow your own vegetables and fruit or did you buy it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. My husband was no gardener. We bought all our vegetables and fruit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Any tinned or dried vegetables did you buy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I used to buy the dried apricots to make the apricot jam but that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you keep any hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Or pigs or goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Never had room for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember how many times a week you ate meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
We used to have half a leg of lamb for Sunday, and that used to be cold. My husband was fond of cold meat and pickled onions, and potatoes whole. He always liked them whole, not mashed. Then minced Wednesday. Liver f
or Thursday and sometimes fish for Friday - he was fond of fish.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about tinned meat - did you have any tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Never bought tinned stuff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you get any extra meat from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We didn't get extra meat at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you had meat most days, did you, except when you had fish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever feel that you had to go short sometimes so that your husband and daughter could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We usually shared alike.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your husband have a larger helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No he wasn't a big eater really.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about table manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was your daughter allowed to talk during meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Could she choose to eat what she wanted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. She used to have just the same as we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Supposing she left something uneaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well she never had too much to leave really, we used to generally manage how she'd eat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You knew what she wanted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 If she wanted salt, for instance, could she ask for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Or a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you teach her to hold her knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 To sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes she always had to behave herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was she allowed to bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Not at meal times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Could she leave the table whenever she liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. She didn't have to leave the table 'til she was finished. 'Til we was finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you sit in the same places at table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We always kept our own places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And you served the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When your little girl was too young to feed herself, did you feed her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 At the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you feed her first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. At the table. Just give her some as well as ourselves you see, in between.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you feel there was a right and a wrong way of bringing up children, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well yes. I don't think you should spoil children and let them think they're so much different to anything else. We was never brought up any different. So I took it the same as I was brought up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about your husband? Did you have the same ideas about bringing up your children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 He never interfered. He never bothered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You didn't discuss this together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 If you were worried about your little girl at any time, who would you talk to about her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well she used to have everything that was going. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9399718\charrsid10698579 Measles}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  and that sort of thing like the rest of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you see your mother often before you left Luton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I lived near handy to her you see, about ten minutes walk away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever ask her advice in bringing up the little girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would you think you and she had the same ideas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about your husband's mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I didn't know his mo
ther. My mother did. She said she was a very nice person. And of course his father used to be a Sunday School teacher in the church.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Can you tell me some of the things you felt you ought to do for your daughter? Did you feel you had to show her affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No. I didn't. Because we never had time for that. We was all treated the same at home and so of course we took it just natural. You're all together so long as you see that they're alright you don't pay to fuss them too much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about her safety - did you ever feel worried about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. She was a child that always wanted to be home and read. She used to do a lot of reading I never had any worry at all with her.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Supposing that she was naughty sometimes, did you feel that you ought to discipline her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes. I'd tell her she'd get a jolly good hiding if she didn't behave herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Supposing she was upset about something, would she come and share her worry with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. She'd just tell me, you see, and I'd say "Never mind, you don't want to take any notice."
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever manage to leave her in the evenings so that you could go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No I never left her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you didn't have a neighbour or relative who came in to look after her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We was always taught to keep your own business to yourself and to look after and take your own responsibilities.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Supposing as she got older she joined in when the grown ups were talking, was that allowable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well she was never a child like that. She never pushed herself. She used to listen, you see. No. She was always pretty good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What did you bring her up to think was important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 To take care of her money. And she's often said, since she's been older, "Well mum I've always been glad you've br
ought me up to realise the value of money."
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Supposing another child hurt your child, did you tell her she should hit back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No, I used to say, "Keep away from her."
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Were there any children that you discouraged her from playing with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No she didn't go out a lot to play. As long as she'd got a book she was quite happy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 If she was punished for something would it be by you or your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh it would have to be me give her a good talking to,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And would this happen often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. She wasn't any trouble at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would you say that your daughter received the ideas that she had about how to behave from you or from both you and your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well. I should say from both of us really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you never left your little girl with anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Some people think that children should be with the mother all the time, others think it is not necessary and does them good to be with other people quite a lot too. What did you think? at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I don't know. Her dad used to take her for walks when she got older. You know, grown up. They used to go for a lot of walks together.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When your little girl had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes I'd let her have her little friends in to tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would she have a present?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
I used to buy her clothes as a rule, something she really needed, and she used to be quite pleased with them. She didn't have a lot of toys because you couldn't afford to buy toys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did she have anything different to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I used to make some cakes and put some icing on. That was a treat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about Christmas Day? Did you do anything special on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well yes, we used to fill her stocking up with different things she liked. And if ther
e was no clothes she wanted I used to let her have the money, 'cos I knew she could get them if she wanted anything then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you do anything different on Christmas Day?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Only the cooking - that was a full time job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you'd have a big Christmas dinner would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes, we used to have a chicken.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have any musical instruments in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Only a gramophone, you know, with the horn to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did any of you sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well there was only us three you see here. But whe
n we was at home we used to have Sunday evenings. My eldest sister used to play the piano and we all used to meet on Sundays. My eldest brothers used to bring their girls. And I always used to reckon to go home at Christmas - we always used to meet at Chr
istmas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 After you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9326226 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
, was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. We always used to go for Christmas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you play any games with your daughter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. She used to go out with a hoop and skipping and like that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your husband ever play games with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
He used to skip and he used to have a go with her ball and see how many times he could keep bouncing it. He won a cake at a fete once through bouncing it the longest time. (in Guildford)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You said she was very fond of books, so there would be books in the house. Would there be newspapers and magazines as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No we never had magazines, just books.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Where did you get the books from? The library?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 The library - and she still belongs to the library.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you read aloud to her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I never read to her she used to read to herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you take your daughter out visiting neighbours sometimes, or friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I only took her out when we went shopping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did she ever go out shopping without you? With somebody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Sometimes did she go out with her father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes, she often went out with him. He used to take her out with him for walks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What did you do on bank holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Used to go up to St. Marthas, or Newlands Corner. We used to walk there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 That was quite a long way for a little girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes, but we used to manage it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We always used to go home for Christmas, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And how long would you stay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Just for the Christmas time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And that was to meet all your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. I was the only one away from home you see. It was a reunion.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Can you remember how you spent Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Shopping really. We didn't get our wages, you see, not 'til Saturdays. Saturday dinner times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you would go shopping on Saturdays and would you take your little girl with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. Because we used to have a good walk, you see, at the same time. I used to go with the pram. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would you put on different clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We didn't make a fuss of ourselves, as long as we was clean, and respectable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 My husband used to like to go fishing. And my little girl used to go to Sunday School, handy, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you have special clothes for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes we always had Sunday clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What did you feel about Sunday, did you think you could do some work or did you think it was wrong to work or to enjoy yourself?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well we used to be pleased when it was Sunday to have a proper rest and make it a Sunday, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was your little girl allowed to play games on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 My husband used to go - he used to go to Stoke Church. And Sunday afternoons he'd go to the Men's Service too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So when did he go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
That was after the war started, you see. He'd go fishing when he had a Sunday off. He was on night work so he only used to get a Sunday evening now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So do you mean that sometimes he had to work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. When the war was on he had to work nights and of course he had Sundays free then, once a month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever go to Church with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 On Sunday mornings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I was always at home (The old fashioned woman) to cook the dinners, there was always a dinner ready for them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So would you go in the afternoon or the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No, I used to just go out with him, you see, we used to go out together in the evening for a little while.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I didn't belong to anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember if the church had a temperance club? Or any other activity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Not that I know of. I never meant in for .... You see I was really a stranger here then. I didn't know anybody really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about your little girl, did she start going to Sunday School when she was old enough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did she go to Church with you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 She used to go with her dad mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did she go to Sunday School by herself at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have grace at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We didn't have time for that really 'cause things were just natural.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was your little girl taught to say prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 It was sort of natural for her really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So she always did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. They taught her at school, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you take any interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I left that to the men.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 He never used to say much about it. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you don't know what party he would have supported?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. He was never a man to argue or anything like that. Pretty quiet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember voting in a General Election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You don't know what your husband would have voted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever feel that you or your husband were under any pressure from anybody to vote for a particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You weren't a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And your husband wouldn't be pressurised to vote a certain way by his employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When you and your husband were not working, how did you spend your leisure time together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 We used to go for walks but I could never walk too far, really, it used to knock me up a bit. But I used to try and keep it 
up with the rest of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever go out together in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What time did your husband get home from work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well you see he lived on top of the works really. We were quite close to Dennis's you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You didn't spend much time travelling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. And I would never want to go out a lot. I was quite happy with my home and doing my jobs, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What time did the work finish at the factory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 About }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9399718\charrsid10698579 six\rquote  o\rquote clock}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So he'd be home soon after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. He only used to have to go through the garden and he was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what would he do after he'd had his meal, would he stay at home or would he go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No, he'd go and he'd sit and look at the traffic on the by-pass. He always felt he must b
e out because it was so oily and smelly in the factory, he was glad to be quiet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did he go to any clubs or evening institutes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. He used to sometimes just go back up the club and play billiards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What club would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Dennis's - they had just a small one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would they have a license there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I expect so, I didn't interest myself, with anything like that, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did he ever go to the pub for a drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No he didn't believe in that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you didn't have the opportunity to go out together very much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well he didn't go drinking. His pleasure was just fishing when he had the chance
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you belong to any savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You said your husband was interested in fishing, what about you, apart from walking, did you have any other interests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Well when he went fishing I was always at home so that I had a nice meal ready for him when he got home. And he used to say, "Well mate, this is lovely, I never thought of coming home to this."
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did either of you ever bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Sometimes he'd put something on the Derby, like they all did, at the factory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was he interested in racing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well he was, but it never interested me much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about theatres, or concerts or cinemas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well he 
used to like to go to the theatre and to the repertory and we used to have a nice little theatre here you know. We had all the latest plays, and it was really nice. Enjoyed that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes I liked the theatre but I didn't like the repertory. I didn't like the waiting in between while they was moving the things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you go to the cinema at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. I used to go there rather than the repertory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about the music hall, were you fond of music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well not too bad, he used to like the classical music. He often used to whistle that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did he ever go to a concert?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you keep any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 My daughter always had a cat. She was fond of cats. Nice w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8943772\charrsid10698579 hite}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579  pussy cat, you know \{ILLEGIBLE\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have a gardening?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you all work in it or just your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well it was clay, you know. It was hard work. My husband couldn't do much not with the digging.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you garden much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I used to try and do a bit, you see. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You didn't have many friends that you would go out with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I never made the idea of going out. There was me home and looking after me home and I was always there with the meals on time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So that was really your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 That was my life. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did anyone outside the home help you sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well my mother was good when the 'slack' time came. She had my daughter to live there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 When you said 'slack' time, was that when there wasn't work for your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. After the wa
r, see, we had twelve months of one week on and one off. And then fifteen months of nothing. We had 25/- a week. We used to have 2/- a week to keep a child those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 If you ever had to stay in bed how did you manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well my husband. Or a neighbour perhaps would come in - but they never seemed to bother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You managed by yourself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 You didn't have any relations living near you then did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Nobody at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your husband have some friends that might help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
No. He was never one like that. He was always just alone fishing, you know. He never went anywhere. He didn't have friends. He liked to be free.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So it would be unusual for friends to come into the house and be entertained?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh I never had that. I couldn't afford entertaining. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did your neighbours ever come in to see you - just pop in and out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
One would. She'd come in next door and she'd say get your cup and your milk out and I've brought you a cup of tea. And there used to be just the tea pot, you know. You had your own cup and milk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you go and see her too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. Not unless she was ill or anything. I never run in there like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusements. Did you ever g
et together with any friends for music or games or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. I was one of those proper dull people - always glad to rest. And stay at home. And I was fond of reading.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. 10/6 a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. He used to come every Monday for the rent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What was he like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well he wasn't a very nice sort of man really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I was glad as soon as he'd come and gone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you feel he was uninterested in you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
I used to keep the place nice but he used to say "I wish you'd move then I could let this for more money." That's why I didn't like him. It was well and clean you see and that's why he'd like to ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Only knitting. I used to make all my husband's socks, and the girl's socks. Knit her cardigans, you see, and me own things, and his pullovers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you knit for yourself too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you collect anything in your family? Were you interested in collecting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 
Now I'd like to ask you about the social community where you lived. Can you tell me who you thought were the most important people in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Nobody as I know of, because I never asked for anything from anyone. I just managed and made the best of things whatever turned up.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 So you didn't come into contact with people other than yourselves really, and people like yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about the shopkeepers, did you know any of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I used to go up to the butchers, we had a butchers handy, you see, and I used to pay for everything as I had it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did he think of himself as more important than perhaps you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. He was very nice. Homely. Pleased to see you really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you know any of the clergy, or teachers or farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. We never went anywhere to get to know anyone you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever meet the employers at Dennis's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well we used to when we had the Christmas parties. They had one f
or the children and we used to go up and sometimes meet them. My husband started dancing - he went with the girl when she got old enough, he took her up to learn the dancing and he went up as well. And I thought well if they're going I might as well so th
at's when I started.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would that be at Dennis's club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. They used to have it one evening a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And then I suppose if the employers of Dennis's were there they would be the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. That's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 How did you feel about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well they was all nice. All seemed very nice what you met. The heads and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What sort of people would you say went to the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well about like ourselves. They was all about the same sort of people, those days. We all seemed about the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 What about the clergyman would he seem different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 They was all nice, homely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you have any experience of the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Not as I got older, no. Only when I was young. Just a kiddy like.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Would you say the people around you had the same standard of living as yourselves, or were there different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Oh no, they all seemed natural, you know, just homely everyday people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Much the same as yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Do you remember if there was a distinction between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No there was no difference, we didn't take no notice really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you feel that some people were rough and some people were respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No, because they all lived round about, you see, those that worked at Dennis's you knew them, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 It was a housing estate belonging to Dennis's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. They had a housing estate as the years went by, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And did you know anybody else apart from the people on the housing estate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No I never bothered, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you have a struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well that's natural, isn't it. When you've got just your husband's wages coming in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Can you remember what you felt about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well I'd always been used to managing and I made myself manage. I never borrowed from anybody or had anything without I paid for it.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And what difference did it make when your husband was ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Well it did make a difference then, you see, because at that time they had the unemployment money for a little while.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 I see. That would be after 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Yes. That was late years you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Was he ever out of work in the early days when you first came to Guildford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 And he wasn't ill then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15484881 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 Did you ever have any help from the Guardians, the parish or a charity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12995975 BI  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12664204\charrsid10698579 No. It was unthought of. Nobody did them days, no.
\par }}